- `ihr : t₂.size < 2 ^ t₂.height`

I know that `2 ^ (1 + max t₁.height t₂.height) = 2 * 2 ^ max t₁.height t₂.height`.

Since `max t₁.height t₂.height ≥ t₁.height`, we have `2 ^ max t₁.height t₂.height ≥ 2 ^ t₁.height`.
